Name: flask-fool
Version: 1.0.6
Summary:  A Flask extension that prevents browser access to API. 
Home-page: https://github.com/Faylixe/flask-fool
Author: Felix Voituret
Author-email: felix@voituret.fr
License: Apache Licence 2.0
